OL,3,CHigh temperatures could mean hottest
OL,4,Cbank holiday on record
OL,6,FMonday is forecast to be the hottest
OL,7,Fbank holiday on record with "historic"
OL,8,Ftemperatures of 34C predicted in
OL,9,FGreater London and south-east England.
OL,11,FIt comes after the UK saw its hottest
OL,12,FMay day for at least 79 years on
OL,13,FSunday with a high of 32.3C at Kew
OL,14,FGardens in south-west London.
OL,26,@oD@]OUoD@fO]
