OL,3,CHigh temperatures could mean hottest
OL,4,Cbank holiday on record
OL,6,FScotland saw highs of 23.5C in
OL,7,FEdinburgh on Sunday, just below the
OL,8,Fcurrent record of 23.6C recorded in
OL,9,FAboyne on May 1.
OL,11,FThe Met Office said heatwave
OL,12,Fconditions were met in eight parts of
OL,13,FEngland on Sunday ` Heathrow in
OL,14,FGreater London, Benson in Oxfordshire,
OL,15,FBrooms Barn in Suffolk, High Beech in
OL,16,FEssex, Kew Gardens in London, Northolt
OL,17,Fin London, Santon Downham in Suffolk
OL,18,Fand Writtle in Essex.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
