OL,3,CHigh temperatures could mean hottest
OL,4,Cbank holiday on record
OL,6,FLincolnshire Police said the body of
OL,7,F15-year-old Declan Sawyer was
OL,8,Frecovered from the water at Swanholme
OL,9,FLakes, Lincoln, after he was reported
OL,10,Fto be in trouble at 2.30pm on Sunday.
OL,12,FAlthough Monday is set to be hot for
OL,13,Fmany parts of England, north-west
OL,14,FScotland will be breezier and damper
OL,15,Fwith thicker clouds.
OL,17,FSaturday was the first time this year
OL,18,Fthat the UK had passed 30C and Sunday
OL,19,Fsaw the hottest recorded May
OL,20,Ftemperature since 1947.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
