OL,3,CHigh temperatures could mean hottest
OL,4,Cbank holiday on record
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fissued its first amber health alert of
OL,8,F2026 on Friday, warning that there is
OL,9,Fa risk of a significant impact across
OL,10,Fhealth and social care services. The
OL,11,Falert will remain in place until
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FThe heat is considered to be dangerous
OL,15,Ffor some vulnerable groups including
OL,16,Folder adults as their bodies struggle
OL,17,Fto regulate temperature.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
